The paper presents a method for discovering governing differential equations from data using machine learning techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves numerical analysis (cs.NA) and control systems (cs.SY) as it deals with differential equations. The use of genetic programming and automatic differentiation also suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE).
